Qv9Ggg8tyEA.title: HHr || Goodbye Harmony
Qv9Ggg8tyEA.description:
The Story of Friendship, Love and Sacrifice that all of us had witnessed growing up. This video is my way of coming into terms with one of the biggest disappointment in my life which is the Harry and Hermione Pairing not going beyond what is platonic. But since the HHr shipper in me prevails, I pooled all the Deathly Hallows clip I can find all over youtube and made a story line around it and I came up with this:

Ron left despite Hermione's pleas. In her loneliness, Harry comforts her. And in this moment of weakness, they created a life. A life, that despite hesitance, Hermione was willing to raise with Harry, as she accepts his offer of marriage. And at that moment, Harry promises to provide Hermione and their future family a happy life. Hermione tells him that she is happy but her emotions shows other wise. Just when everything was to be well, Ron shows up and tells Hermione how he truly feels about her. Hermione doesn't react and Harry, although bothered with Ron's reappearance assures himself that he and Hermione still have their future together because of the baby. When Death Eaters attack however, Hermione is captured and tortured. In the whole ordeal, she loses the baby. Harry sits devastated but as he looks back on everything, he stands firm in his decision to marry Hermione because he was in love with her. When he tells her this, she does not give him the reply he wanted from her. Instead, she runs out and Harry, well, he could only stand from a distance and watch, as Hermione chooses Ron over him. 

"And. For a moment. I thought that she chose me. But she didn't."

Seeing Hermione with Ron was something that he could not bare, so he turns and leaves. 

"And so I said. Goodbye."

I wrote this because I detest the idea that Harry and Hermione don't even react negatively or even show any tinge of jealousy whenever the other shows affection to their Canon Pairs. I wanted to believe that Harry and Hermione had gone through something so deep and so life changing that it pains them to be together. And, that in their desperation to escape what they had gone through, decided to accept other people's love instead of each other' s. 

P. S. Seriously, while editing this video and going over scenes when Ron enters the picture, I was taken aback as to how much I wanted to remove his SMUG of a face from his neck. Honestly, Ron and Hermione: NOT A  VERY GOOD-LOOKING COUPLE. GOD! NOT IN A MILLION YEARS.

+First Place in Best Emotion
Harry Potter Epic Contest (Londonexplore101 )

hKw7kVcEzSU.title: Jugador de futbol recibe un golpe despues del partido
hKw7kVcEzSU.description:
El volante de Instituto de Córdoba Gastón Machín sufrió ayer una seria agresión del defensor Mariano Barale, de Guillermo Brown, quien le asestó un golpe en el pómulo derecho que le provocó un corte, el cual debió ser suturado con ocho puntos.

El "arañazo" se produjo al término del partido que el equipo de Córdoba y el de Chubut igualaron 1-1 en el marco de la octava fecha del campeonato de la B Nacional que tiene a ambos clubes en el fondo de la tabal con ocho y siete puntos, respectivamente.

El partido tuvo un alto voltaje durante los 90 minutos con cruces picantes entres varios jugadores a partir de las decisiones arbitrales de Sergio Testa. Apenas finalizado el encuentro hubo, según relatan los jugadores de Instituto, una provocación de Andrés Ylliana, hoy entrenador de Guillermo Brown, que desató la batahola en la que el principal perjudicado fue justamente el jugador Machín, como se aprecia en la imagen que subió en su cuenta de Twitter Nicolás Di Fiore, jefe de prensa del club Instituto de Córdoba.

Como si esto fuera poco, el jugador agredido recibió la expulsión por parte del árbitro. Los dirigentes esperan por informe final de Testa para presentar el descargo.

HTOO26cCCx0.title: Nerdy News: Angry Birds Christmas Lights
HTOO26cCCx0.description:
http://www.videogamesblogger.com/2011/12/25/angry-birds-christmas-lights.htm     What do you think? Is video game preservation a waste of taxpayer's dollars? Are video game culturally significant? Would you have liked to learn video game coding and design when you were in elementary school? Is it a fun way for kids to become more tech-savy? Would you ever make a holiday light display that is video game themed?

As far as video game deals, Amazon is still running a Buy 1, Get 1 40% Off off sale on over 400 Xbox 360, PS3, Nintendo Wii, DS, PSP, PC and Mac video games priced $19.99 and under.  This video game sale features Mass Effect 2, The Orange Box, Halo 3 ODST, Red Dead Redemption: The Undead Nightmare, plus more! Amazon also has a Kinect bundle available with Kinect Adventures, Gunstringer, and Fruit Ninja for only $99.99. For those big spenders The Playstation 3D Display is discounted to $399.99, a savings of $100. This 24" Edge LED display comes bundled with a pair of PlayStation Active Shutter 3D glasses, a HDMI cable, and a copy of MotorStorm: Apocalypse.

Is Saving Video Game History A Waste Of Money? Some people, mostly gamers, think that preserving video game history is important because of the cultural impact that games have had on modern society. According to U.S. Senator Tom Coburn, who identified a $113,277 grant issued to Rochester's International Center for the History of Electronic Games as being among 100 "unnecessary, duplicative and low-priority projects" that the U.S. federal government spent money on in 2011. That sounds like a lot of "bah, humbug" to me. The grant was given to establish the best practices for conserving electronic artifacts for museums, libraries, and other organizations.

An afterschool program called TechGYRLS, had the elementary school kids in the program present games they made themselves at a recent TechEXPO. The girls were led by a group of teachers who decided to try something different from the usual PowerPoint projects. Instead, teacher Jackie Zabel said they decided to have the students create video games and play with coding and animation using Mac laptops and MicroWorlds EX software. The teachers said it was rewarding to see the students learn computer confidence and win the support and encouragement of family members. They feel it is especially important to encourage young girls to be more interested in technology.

Not only is this Holiday light display gamerific, it's also actually playable! the original game had loose physics and required experimentation, but this version will involve even more trial and error because the birds are invisible. The game is played using a slingshot-shaped controller with three buttons, one each to aim to the left, right and center. The power of the shot depends on how long you hold down a button. The whole thing is done using over 20,000 lights, and a bunch of Light-o-rama controllers. It even broadcasts audio on a low-wattage FM transmitter so people driving by in their cars can hear the sounds. Pretty amazing, in my book.

Just Dance 3 is a music video game released on the Wii, PlayStation 3, and Xbox 360, with Move and Kinect support. Along with solos and duets, Just Dance 3 features quartets which allows 4 players to dance all together, as well as playlists that group songs together.

Minecraft is focused on creativity and building, allowing players to build constructions out of textured cubes in a 3D world. Gameplay in its commercial release has two principal modes: Survival, which requires players to acquire resources themselves and maintain their health and hunger; and Creative, where the player has an unlimited supply of resources, the ability to fly, and no concept of health or hunger. A third gameplay mode, named Hardcore, is essentially the same as Survival, but the difficulty is locked on the hardest setting and respawning is disabled, forcing the player to delete his or her world upon death. An outdated Classic version is also available for free, although it is no longer being developed. Creative Minecraft resembles Classic, but with many more features.

Ti8XCKpIr7Y.description: ร้าน ช.กลการยานยนต์ หรือ CKK RACING  อีกหนึ่งความภาคภูมิใจของชาวแปดริ้วที่ดูแลชาวแปดริ้วมาอย่างยาวนานทั้งเรื่องของการให้บริการด้าน ช่วงล่างรถยนต์ ไม่ว่าจะเป็นระบเบรค  ล้อแม็ก ยาง  และการปรับแต่งต่างๆ ซึ่ง CKK RACING ให้บริการด้วยความจริงใจ ให้คำแนะนำอย่างเป็นกันเอง  สำหรับชาวแปดริ้วและผู้ที่ชื่นชอบการแต่งรถฟลาดไม่ได้นะครับ ที่จะสนับสนุนกิจการของคนแปดริ้ว   CKK RACING เปิดบริการทุกวัน ทั้ง 2สาขา ตั้งอยู่ ถ.ศิริโสธร (ฉะเชิงเทรา-บางประกง) ใกล้สถานีขนส่ง เยื้อง BIG C ฉะเชิงเทรา
